{"id":"428835640537739_565859136835388","type":"photo","created_time":"2013-11-01T14:35:06+0000","message":"Shibir slates media lies against it:\r\n\r\nSome mass media protecting culprits blaming Shibir falsely and enviously- Chhatrashibir\r\n\r\n\r\nBangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir strongly slated and gainsaid false and baseless reports thereupon aired by some dailies like Prothom Alo, Somokal, Jaijaidin, Amader Somoy etc under the heading \u201cShibir cut tendons of BCL leader in Bogra\u201d and by Banglanews under the heading \u201cShibir threatens Rokeya University VC of death\u201d.\r\n\r\nIn a gainsaying statement, the Secretary-General of Bangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir Abdul Zabbar said, \u201cThe student segment got heavily dumbfounded to see some mass media publish, out of their habitual slavery, reports devoid of any certain evidentiary documents against Chhatrashibir regarding the attack on Chhatra League leader in Bogra. The reporters prepared the reports just basing on the statements of Chhatra League leaders and this fact proves that these reports are nothing but a sequel to anti-Shibir propaganda. The reports are full of false statements given by BCL leaders including \u2018Shibir men cut tendons of Chhatra League leader after attacking on him\u2019 but eyewitnesses and police personnel couldn\u2019t mention any single name of Shibir activists.\u201d\r\n\r\nHe urged the concerned media and media men to stop publishing false and fabricated reports any more in future.","picture":"https:\/\/fbcdn-photos-d-a.akamaihd.net\/hphotos-ak-ash4\/1379787_565859113502057_10592239_s.jpg"}